<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wernher <expan>Parsperg<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        ritter, hauptman czu der Freyenstat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Wernher, uns hat <expan>furg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
            Paulus Voͤrchtel, unser lieber burger, von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> muter <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie ir dem Hans
            Seger von <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan>verryden, irem armman, sein vihe genomen habt und
            niht <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt, daz er ir armman sey. Also hat der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> vor uns zu den <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt,
            daz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Seg<ex>er</ex></expan> ir armman sey und den mit tür und tor besliesze. Hyrümb
                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im <expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan> sein vihe
                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan> post Galli.</ab>
</div>
